Title: Vesna va veloce
Writer: Umberto Contarello, Carlo Mazzacurati, Sandro Petraglia, Claudio Piersanti, Stefano Rulli
Actors: Tereza Groszmannová, Antonio Albanese, Silvio Orlando, Ivano Marescotti
Plot: A young Eastern European girl ditches the rest of her tour group to embark upon a new life in Italy. Though she writes friends and family glowing accounts of her fabulous adventures in her adopted home, the truth is much more tragic.
